{"tid":2263278,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"宮鵬被揭曾參與統戰部研習 學習總書記習近平精神及中共領導制度等","createTime":"2020-10-29T18:23:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T09:00:34.000Z","uid":240362,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e7cec9713e6945b323f347837d4e6c4c841ec626","tid":2263278,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T18:23:44.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】港大校委會周二大比數通過委任兩名內地學者申作軍及宮鵬擔任副校長。網媒眾新聞昨報道，發現清華大學理學院院長宮鵬雖被中共黨報《光明日報》列為「無黨派人士」，但他三年前曾參加中共中央統戰部組織、在中央社會主義學院的「無黨派人士理論研究班」，學習中共總書記習近平精神及中共領導制度等，亦曾說：「作為新一代中國讀書人，從說到寫到行動，要全面捍衞國家尊嚴。」<br />\n<br />\n港大社會科學院前院長卜約翰稱，內地大學對學系領導層級黨委名單等網頁一般小心處理，港大卻說成清華網頁出錯，說法不太可信，料中共幹部或黨委書記派駐大學及不同機構可能成為新常態。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201030/YP4XNUHJ6FDVRMTRMDIEP7YJAA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201030%2FYP4XNUHJ6FDVRMTRMDIEP7YJAA%2F&d=L3LYojiCq%2FWCCnzMgLa5KIbsTeectjBlsojPGUwt5kI%3D&h=e11e1117\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201030%2FYP4XNUHJ6FDVRMTRMDIEP7YJAA%2F&h=9d5a9029\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201030/YP4XNUHJ6FDVRMTRMDIEP7YJAA/</a>"},{"pid":"82a63c897747b26e65df4e293165b96a7e233612","tid":2263278,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T18:24:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eef20c5aac52be09fc25ec644efd0833467d738","tid":2263278,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T18:27:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4372d47cdebea2